Intial Version

  - User thread based on context switch of unix / linux / osx
  - Inter communication between threads made ease
  - Semaphore
  - Threads with attributes on initialization.
  - And state of the art thread schedules with proprietary algorithm
  - C++11 compliance
  - Small footprint memory
  - No  limitations for ammount of threads
  - Capable of useing various thread container
  - Kernel is the main thread container, but others cam be created and used together.
  - Safe Sleep and SELECT (for non blocking i/o use and error handler)

  51% done till now
